column9: Please take a few minutes to fill out the following questionnaire. This questionnaire borrows from a series of questions that are meant to allow you to self-assess your previous behavior as it relates to time, money, relationships, and logic. The intent of this survey is to inform us about your background as a professional in your field, and meant to guide our ongoing research in understanding personalities. This survey will not be tactically used for other than informational purposes in guiding our understanding of your field. Lastly, the survey collects no personal data beyond general demographic details and we will only use aggregated anonymous data to draw conclusions.

column52: Congrats, you've finished the survey! Thank you for taking the time to give us your invaluable responses. If you are interested in learning more, the survey leveraged several widely used survey measures from ongoing social and behavioral science research from Frederick (2005), Toplak, West, & Stanovich (2014), and Kahneman and Tversky (1992). Please feel free to reach out to us if you have any questions and would like to understand the behavioral science work we do: https://creativescience.co/contact-us/
